ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of MELODY J. McLEOD of Yellowknife, Northwest Territories, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Nature to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective June 21, 2005, in the place of Jane Dragon.
